#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; offers you the possibility to have several virtual desktops."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the names to the desktops by clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Rename</guibutton> button (appears when you hover the desktop "
"item in the list) and entering text into the text field."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to remove a desktop, use the trash overlay icon at the right of "
"the desktop item."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button to add a virtual desktop "
"(default name is <guilabel>New Desktop</guilabel>) to the list."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the number of rows in the pager item on the panel. Just "
"use the rows input box below the list to adjust the number of desktops. The "
"desktops will be rearranged by the rows automatically."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation wraps around"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option if you want a keyboard or active desktop border "
"navigation beyond the edge of a desktop to take you to the opposite edge of "
"the new desktop."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show animation when switching"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Slide</guilabel>, <guilabel>Desktop Cube Animation</"
"guilabel>, or <guilabel>Fade Desktop</guilabel> from the drop-down box or "
"switch animations off by unchecking the item. If the selected animation has "
"settings options, click on the tools icon on the right of the drop-down box "
"to launch a configuration dialog."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show on-screen display when switching"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option if you want to have an on-screen display for desktop "
"switching."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show desktop layout indicators"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabling this option will show a small preview of the desktop layout "
"indicating the selected desktop."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you enable <guilabel>Mouse wheel over desktop switches desktop</"
#| "guilabel> then scrolling the wheel over an empty space on the desktop "
#| "will change the the next virtual desktop numerically, in the direction "
#| "you scrolled (either up or down)."
